column2: nine times outta ten I go for the green eggs. My stomach is a bottomless pit so I usually ask for an extra egg. You can and should ask for the biscuits instead of the toast. Simply Divine. It also comes with spicy fried potato cubes which do more than just provide filler. If you want freshly squeezed orange juice
column3: they have that as well. There is usually a wait
column4: which can be oppressive in the Houston summertime
column5: but I find it worth the agony.
